.
One of our students today played her violin 🎻 for us and showed us all the violin parts. 
.
Her performance sparked conversations about other instruments, composers and different music genres. 
.
It is always a great opportunity as well to teach grace and courtesy. The lessons show up in unexpected ways sometimes , all we have to do is follow the child. 🌱

